article_id:156,category_name:News,title_name:Added High Brunhilda's Trial to the Advanced Dragon Trials!,image_path:,message:<div>We have added High Brunhilda&#39;s Trial to the Advanced Dragon Trials even quests on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1545026400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/62885bb44bebef1f890454ed67403d3b.png"></div><div>Steel yourself and challenge the mistress of crimson!</div><div><br></div><div><strong>[Changes accompanying the release of High Brunhild&#39;s Trial]</strong></div><div><br></div><div><strong>1. High Brunhilda was added to the Advanced Dragon Trials section of the Treasure Trade menu.</strong></div><div><br></div><div>■Stats</div><div>・Lv 100/100</div><div>・HP 350</div><div>・Strength 120</div><div>・Might 1070</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon details</div><div>The form of the Flamewyrm Brunhilda after releasing her hidden powers. Wreathed in crimson fire, she incinerates anything in range&mdash; except, of course, for the Prince, for whom the flames of love burn even hotter.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>■Skills</div><div>・Crimson Inferno</div><div>Deals flame damage to enemies directly ahead, and inflicts burn.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>■Abilities</div><div>・(Flame) Strength &amp; HP +30%</div><div>If the user is attuned to Flame: increases Strength &amp; HP by 30%.</div><div>・Dragon Time +20%</div><div>Extends shapeshift time by 20%.</div><div><br></div><div>Note: These are the stats when at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>2. The Volcanic Queen wyrmprint was added to the Imperial Onslaught section of the Treasure Trade menu.</strong></div><div><br></div><div>■Abilities</div><div>・High Brunhilda Res +25%, Brunhilda Res +20%, Flame Res +5%</div><div><br></div><div>Note: These are the stats when at maximum level and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>3. Changes to the Challenge Events UI</strong></div><div><br></div><div>・A new Advanced Dragon Trials section was added in the Challenge Events menu, containing both the High Midgardsormr and High Brunhilda Trials.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. A team Might of 13000 or above is required to take on the High Brunhilda Trial.</div><div>2. You must clear Brunhilda&#39;s Trial in Master difficulty before attempting High Brunhilda&#39;s Trial</div><div>3. You must clear Ch. 2 / 2-1 (Normal) to participate in Co-op Play.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1545026400,update_time1545026566